Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:53.70,Default,/,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HEEECE7&} 改变...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:54.70,Default,/,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HEEECE7&} 魔法少女...
