Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:56.32,Default,/,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HEEECE7&} 改变...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:57.82,Default,/,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HEEECE7&} 到神滨市来...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:58.58,Default,/,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HEEECE7&} 命运...
